1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,000
Shut up, young lady!

2
00:00:05,230 --> 00:00:08,730
Mr. Taurus, I need you to leave my wife alone.

3
00:00:08,730 --> 00:00:14,140
Mr. White, there's been a horrible misunderstanding.

4
00:00:15,140 --> 00:00:20,179
It's been a long day, and I'm sure you and Charlotte are very tired.

5
00:00:20,179 --> 00:00:25,239
Maybe you should go home and get a nice, good night's rest.

6
00:00:25,239 --> 00:00:31,620
And tomorrow we can meet, and we can talk about the partnership between the White family and the Taurus family.

7
00:00:31,620 --> 00:00:33,619
How's that sound?

8
00:00:33,619 --> 00:00:36,619
Mr. Taurus, I don't listen to the likes of you.

9
00:00:36,619 --> 00:00:40,619
Charlotte makes the calls. I'll do whatever she wishes.

10
00:00:40,619 --> 00:00:48,939
I bet you will. Get out of my way.

11
00:00:48,939 --> 00:00:53,100
Charlotte, are you all right? Do I need to cancel the magazine interview happening in 10 minutes?

12
00:00:53,100 --> 00:00:59,100
No, I'm all right. This would be a good opportunity to clear any lingering rumors and fix their stock prices.

13
00:00:59,100 --> 00:01:00,100
Good.

14
00:01:00,100 --> 00:01:11,560
I'm sorry. I can explain everything that just happened.

15
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:18,260
The partnership between the White and Taurus families will guarantee to raise both of our stock prices.

16
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:23,260
And it's just a matter of time till these silly little rumors fade.

17
00:01:23,260 --> 00:01:29,420
I promise you will have the freedom to do as you please for the rest of your life.

18
00:01:29,420 --> 00:01:33,609
This is only about the Taurus group. It has nothing to do with you.

19
00:01:33,609 --> 00:01:39,090
Nothing to do with me? You're my wife. You're a problem.

